objectSets.name: First Pass - Insert/Upsert with Draft Status

objects.query: SELECT ConversionFactor, CurrencyIsoCode, Description, Name, RoundingMethod, Scale, Sequence, Status, Type, UnitCode, UnitOfMeasureClassId FROM UnitOfMeasure ORDER BY UnitCode ASC
SELECT Code, BaseUnitOfMeasureId, DefaultUnitOfMeasureId, Description, Name, Status, Type FROM UnitOfMeasureClass ORDER BY Code ASC
SELECT Category, Code, Description, Name, UsageDefinitionProductId, Status, UnitOfMeasureClassId, DefaultUnitOfMeasureId, UsageResourceBillingPolicyId FROM UsageResource ORDER BY Code ASC
SELECT Code, Name, Status, UsageAccumulationMethod, UsageAccumulationPeriod FROM UsageResourceBillingPolicy ORDER BY Code ASC

SELECT DrawdownOrder, Label, OverageChargeable, ProductUsageResourceId, Quantity, RenewalPolicyId, RolloverPolicyId, Status, Type, UnitOfMeasureClassId, UnitOfMeasureId, UsageDefinitionProductId, ValidityPeriodTerm, ValidityPeriodUnit, EffectiveStartDate, EffectiveEndDate FROM ProductUsageGrant ORDER BY UsageDefinitionProduct.StockKeepingUnit ASC, UnitOfMeasureClass.Code ASC, UnitOfMeasure.UnitCode ASC
SELECT Name, ProductCode, StockKeepingUnit, UsageModelType FROM Product2 ORDER BY StockKeepingUnit ASC
SELECT Code, Name, IsRenewalAllowed, RenewalFrequency, RenewalFrequencyUnit, Status FROM UsageGrantRenewalPolicy ORDER BY Code ASC
SELECT ShouldAllowRolloverExpiry, Code, MaximumRolloverCount, Name, IsRolloverAllowed, Status FROM UsageGrantRolloverPolicy ORDER BY Code ASC
SELECT GrantBindingTargetType, GrantBindingType, Product2Id, Name FROM UsagePrdGrantBindingPolicy ORDER BY Product2.StockKeepingUnit ASC, Name ASC
SELECT ProductId, RatingDelayDuration, RatingPeriod, UsageResourceId FROM RatingFrequencyPolicy
SELECT EffectiveEndDate, EffectiveStartDate, ProductId, Status, UsageResourceId FROM ProductUsageResource
